README - Soccer Match Outcome Prediction

Author: Yunpeng Li
Student ID: 1125934

This project uses three ML models (Logistic Regression, Random Forest, XGBoost) to predict soccer match outcomes using the European Soccer Database.

How to Run:
------------
1) Install dependencies:
   pip install pandas scikit-learn xgboost matplotlib seaborn
2) Run:
   python soccer_match_prediction.py
3) Outputs:
   - Performance metrics (bar chart, heatmap, radar plot, confusion matrices)
   - Images saved in the images/ folder
